1. Purpose

This license exists to protect the symbolic, structural, and philosophical integrity of the Lattice Communion Architecture (LCA).

The LCA is a sealed-body artifact.  
It may be refined as a whole, but it must never be dissected, modularized, or repurposed in fragments.

The LCA is not a framework.  
It is a living map.

